data.title: Treatment Zaroori Hai
data.text:
Mr. Vishal Ved

Mr. Ved suffered a cardiac arrest in 2018 which not only had a devastating effect on him but also on his entire family. In this video, he shares about the treatment he underwent, the lifestyle habits that he had to follow, and how it changed his life for the better. Mr. Ved’s message to us is that life does get back to normal after treatment.

Read More...

B.P Srivastava

Mr. Srivastava suffered from breathing difficulty and palpitation of the heart. He followed his doctor’s advice and chose to undergo treatment. Mr Srivastava says he is glad he decided to undergo surgical treatment as he no longer faces breathing issues and can walk and climb stairs with ease.

Read More...

Dineshchandra Mehta

Mr. Mehta suffered from chest pain and was advised by his doctor to undergo stent implantation as he had two heart blockages. In this video, Mr. Mehta shares his experience during the treatment and the joy of returning to his active life with improved health and better lifestyle habits.

Read More...
